reviewText: The most effective business people in the world
This DVD won't play in my DVD player.  It seems like some sort of home made DVD, with the purple type backing which is similar to DVD-R or home recordable DVD's.

This is an old movie "by those that knew him best" that is repackaged and sold as a differnt movie.  The movie consists of several people, and his brother Leon, taking about what they remember.  Nothing new, obviously just an attempt to make money from some old artists that briefly played with Hendrix as kids.  A total rip-off
